---
---
<section class="features section-padding" id="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-header text-center">
      <h2 id="features-heading" class="text-primary">Layanan Unggulan</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Kualitas terbaik untuk identitas tim Anda.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="features-grid" role="list">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <article class="feature-card" role="listitem">
        <div class="icon-box" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="48" height="48">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Custom Jersey</h3>
        <p>Full Sublimation dengan detail presisi tinggi untuk tim Anda.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <article class="feature-card" role="listitem">
        <div class="icon-box" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="48" height="48">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.53 16.122a3 3 0 00-5.78 1.128 2.25 2.25 0 01-2.4 2.245 4.5 4.5 0 008.4-2.245c0-.399-.078-.78-.22-1.128zm0 0a15.998 15.998 0 003.388-1.62m-5.043-.025a15.994 15.994 0 011.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 004.764-4.648l3.813-6.843m-11.628 11.628l-8.067-8.067a15.994 15.994 0 011.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 004.764-4.648l3.813-6.843" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Free Design</h3>
        <p>Konsultasi desain sampai puas! Bantu rancang dari nol hingga sempurna.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <article class="feature-card" role="listitem">
        <div class="icon-box" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="48" height="48">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Sablon Manual & Digital</h3>
        <p>Tersedia layanan sablon DTF dan Polyflex dengan kualitas tinggi.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <article class="feature-card" role="listitem">
        <div class="icon-box" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="48" height="48">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Bahan Premium & Jahitan Rapi</h3>
        <p>Menggunakan material berkualitas yang nyaman serta konstruksi jahitan presisi.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 5 -->
      <article class="feature-card" role="listitem">
        <div class="icon-box" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="48" height="48">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Harga Terjangkau</h3>
        <p>Penawaran harga terbaik untuk pembelian dalam partai besar maupun satuan.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 6 -->
      <article class="feature-card" role="listitem">
        <div class="icon-box" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="48" height="48">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V14.25m17.25 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h1.125c.621 0 1.129-.504 1.09-1.124a17.902 17.902 0 00-3.213-9.193 2.056 2.056 0 00-1.58-.86H14.25M16.5 18.75h-2.25m0-11.177v-.958c0-.568-.422-1.048-.987-1.106a48.554 48.554 0 00-10.026 0 1.106 1.106 0 00-.987 1.106v7.635m12-6.677v6.677m0 4.5v-4.5m0 0h-12" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Pengiriman Tepat Waktu</h3>
        <p>Estimasi pengerjaan yang transparan dan jaminan tiba sesuai jadwal.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }
  
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover,
  .feature-card:focus-within {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .icon-box {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
